snippet.title: MrthumpsCeleboots
snippet.description:
Just a place to act as a repository for (mostly) my older clips and such just in case I lose my external media and the likes. No copyright infringement is intended and the majority of my clips are altered enough that they should be covered under fair use. 

Worry not, I'll still be posting clips and such on the various celeboots sites.
